   Classpath Exception. If this license does not meet your requirements,
   other licenses are negotiable.

Distribution

   The full distribution of Preon can be downloaded from
   [1]http://sourceforge.net/projects/preon/. However, it may be easier to
   point Maven to the snapshot repository, at
   [2]http://preon.sourceforge.net/snapshots/. You are allowed to distribute
   Preon through a Maven repository.

References

